Title: Workshop on Electronic Lab Notebooks (ELNs)
Description: This workshop on Electronic Lab Notebooks (ELNs) took place on 18 April from 09:00 to 12:00 at the ‘Landhaus’ Rothenberge, University of Münster. This interactive workshop was aimed at IT staff and was held in English. After a general introduction to ELNs, we covered the selection and implementation process of ELNs.
Keywords: Electronic Lab Notebooks (ELNs) * Data documentation * Research Data Management * Good Research Practice * Collaboration
